1
00:00:07,006 --> 00:00:10,510
(Arisugawa) It seems like no one will tell you, so I'll tell you.

2
00:00:10,510 --> 00:00:12,512
(Arisugawa) You're in the way.

3
00:00:12,512 --> 00:00:17,517
(Koharu) I hate that I won't be able to see Kurosaki-san again.

4
00:00:17,517 --> 00:00:20,019
I'm sure you'll regret it.

5
00:00:20,019 --> 00:00:23,523
(Yao) There are rumors that the two of you are lovers.

6
00:00:23,523 --> 00:00:26,023
It suits you so well.

7
00:00:29,028 --> 00:00:31,028
Sigh…｡

8
00:00:37,537 --> 00:00:39,037
Smartphone) (notification sound)

9
00:00:42,542 --> 00:00:44,542
Mr. Kurosaki...

10
00:00:53,052 --> 00:01:14,007
♬～

11
00:01:14,007 --> 00:01:34,027
♬～

12
00:01:34,027 --> 00:01:49,542
♬～

13
00:01:49,542 --> 00:01:54,542
♬～

14
00:01:55,548 --> 00:01:58,051
I'm going to the convenience store. I forgot to buy something.

15
00:01:58,051 --> 00:02:00,053
(Akihira) Shall we go together?

16
00:02:00,053 --> 00:02:02,555
No, it's okay, I'll be right back.

17
00:02:02,555 --> 00:02:05,492
(Chifuyu) Be careful of strange people.

18
00:02:05,492 --> 00:02:07,494
Yes, I'll go.

19
00:02:07,494 --> 00:02:09,496
(Akihira) It's dark, so be careful.

20
00:02:09,496 --> 00:02:10,996
Yes.

21
00:02:17,003 --> 00:02:19,005
``You haven't noticed, have you? 》

22
00:02:19,005 --> 00:02:22,005
《Chi-chan has a strangely good intuition》

23
00:02:23,510 --> 00:02:26,513
(The sound of running footsteps)

24
00:02:26,513 --> 00:02:36,013
(breathing heavily)

25
00:02:40,527 --> 00:02:42,529
(Kurosaki) Good evening...!

26
00:02:42,529 --> 00:02:44,531
Oh, Mr. Kurosaki?

27
00:02:44,531 --> 00:02:47,033
Ah yes haa...

28
00:02:47,033 --> 00:02:50,036
Um... hide so you don't find out➡

29
00:02:50,036 --> 00:02:53,039
I was running from the hotel where I work.

30
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:56,042
It's okay if you don't be too careful.

31
00:02:56,042 --> 00:02:58,545
People who look like journalists don't come anymore.

32
00:02:58,545 --> 00:03:02,545
Ah, is that so? Then...

33
00:03:05,985 --> 00:03:07,487
Mr. Koharu.

34
00:03:07,487 --> 00:03:09,489
Ah... hey! This time it's too loose.

35
00:03:09,489 --> 00:03:11,491
a….

36
00:03:11,491 --> 00:03:15,995
Excuse me, I'm glad to meet you...

37
00:03:15,995 --> 00:03:17,995
Hehe...

38
00:03:23,503 --> 00:03:26,506
《Mr. Kurosaki, as usual》

39
00:03:26,506 --> 00:03:30,510
"Am I the only one who cares about that? 》

40
00:03:30,510 --> 00:03:32,512
Koharu-san. Ah, yes!

41
00:03:32,512 --> 00:03:34,514
Do you have time on Saturday?

42
00:03:34,514 --> 00:03:36,516
picture…?

43
00:03:36,516 --> 00:03:41,020
The director wants to invite Koharu to the movie's launch.

44
00:03:41,020 --> 00:03:43,022
The gift was so delicious➡

45
00:03:43,022 --> 00:03:45,022
It seems like I would like to thank you.

46
00:03:46,025 --> 00:03:48,528
I'm happy to be invited➡

47
00:03:48,528 --> 00:03:53,533
That includes actors, right?

48
00:03:53,533 --> 00:03:57,036
Is it okay for an ordinary person like me to interfere?

49
00:03:57,036 --> 00:03:59,038
He's an ordinary person.

50
00:03:59,038 --> 00:04:03,476
Koharu is an essential person for that novel.

51
00:04:03,476 --> 00:04:05,476
That's so...

52
00:04:06,980 --> 00:04:10,483
((CURO and you live in different worlds))

53
00:04:10,483 --> 00:04:12,483
((I'll take it away))

54
00:04:13,987 --> 00:04:16,489
Um... Mr. Kurosaki.

55
00:04:16,489 --> 00:04:19,993
About the Minster photo...

56
00:04:19,993 --> 00:04:24,493
Sorry, I'm not very familiar with SNS...

57
00:04:27,500 --> 00:04:29,002
What is that?

58
00:04:29,002 --> 00:04:32,005
No... it's not a big deal.

59
00:04:32,005 --> 00:04:36,505
Well then, since this is your precious invitation, I'll bother you.

60
00:04:41,014 --> 00:04:43,014
Mr. Koharu.

61
00:04:44,517 --> 00:04:47,517
Is there anything you are concerned about?

62
00:04:53,026 --> 00:04:55,028
(yawn)

63
00:04:55,028 --> 00:04:56,529
Are you sleepy?

64
00:04:56,529 --> 00:05:00,033
Sorry, I'm a little sleep deprived, haha...

65
00:05:00,033 --> 00:05:04,470
Kurosaki-san, you're tired, so please get some rest.

66
00:05:04,470 --> 00:05:05,972
picture?

67
00:05:05,972 --> 00:05:07,974
It gets cold at night, so please keep it warm.

68
00:05:07,974 --> 00:05:10,476
Ah, be careful not to drink too much coffee.

69
00:05:10,476 --> 00:05:13,980
We recommend hot milk or hot ginger.

70
00:05:13,980 --> 00:05:16,983
Ah...hehe...｡

71
00:05:16,983 --> 00:05:19,986
Thank you, Koharu-san.

72
00:05:19,986 --> 00:05:21,988
good night.

73
00:05:21,988 --> 00:05:24,490
good night.

74
00:05:24,490 --> 00:05:26,492
Have a nice dream.

75
00:05:26,492 --> 00:05:37,003
♬～

76
00:05:37,003 --> 00:05:40,006
《I'm glad I didn't say that...》

77
00:05:40,006 --> 00:05:45,506
《I don't want to cause unnecessary worry about Mr. Arisugawa》

78
00:05:48,514 --> 00:05:57,023
♬～

79
00:05:57,023 --> 00:05:58,524
Sister...

80
00:05:58,524 --> 00:06:00,526
Ah!

81
00:06:00,526 --> 00:06:02,962
Ah, no, chichichi... that's not it?

82
00:06:02,962 --> 00:06:05,965
Um... Ah, I've been having a big appetite lately!

83
00:06:05,965 --> 00:06:09,469
Isn't this a pattern you created because you can't sleep?

84
00:06:09,469 --> 00:06:12,472
(Natsuki) Hey, can't you sleep?

85
00:06:12,472 --> 00:06:14,974
That's not true! Nene is okay.

86
00:06:14,974 --> 00:06:16,976
Look, Chi-chan and Nacchan both eat a lot.

87
00:06:16,976 --> 00:06:19,979
Delicious food is a source of energy, so yeah.

88
00:06:19,979 --> 00:06:21,981
Yes, Se~no.

89
00:06:21,981 --> 00:06:24,984
(Chifuyu: Natsuki) Itadakimasu...｡

90
00:06:24,984 --> 00:06:27,487
Yes, I'll take it.

91
00:06:27,487 --> 00:06:30,490
《I will try not to lose to Mr. Arisugawa➡

92
00:06:30,490 --> 00:06:32,490
I need to eat well! 》

93
00:06:34,994 --> 00:06:37,997
(Chifuyu)♪~ Hehehehe~

94
00:06:37,997 --> 00:06:39,499
I'm home.

95
00:06:39,499 --> 00:06:41,501
Welcome back.

96
00:06:41,501 --> 00:06:43,002
Yuio-san.

97
00:06:43,002 --> 00:06:46,502
I see, my sister isn't here today.

98
00:06:48,007 --> 00:06:50,507
It was the launch of CURO's movie.

99
00:06:52,011 --> 00:06:56,011
It's just out of place for me to go there.

100
00:06:57,517 --> 00:07:01,020
Are you worried about Koharu being taken away by CURO?

101
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:05,458
But...! My sister is being manipulated somehow.

102
00:07:05,458 --> 00:07:09,462
It's okay, I won't let you do that.

103
00:07:09,462 --> 00:07:10,963
picture?

104
00:07:10,963 --> 00:07:13,466
Oh no, Chifuyu-kun➡

105
00:07:13,466 --> 00:07:15,968
I thought it was my sister after all.

106
00:07:15,968 --> 00:07:17,970
Regular customers have been here for a long time➡

107
00:07:17,970 --> 00:07:19,972
She said she was my older sister's child.

108
00:07:19,972 --> 00:07:21,972
But it's different!

109
00:07:36,990 --> 00:07:38,491
"Are you okay"

110
00:07:38,491 --> 00:07:42,991
《I borrowed a dress from Mika-chan and had her do my makeup》

111
00:07:46,499 --> 00:07:50,503
(Yanagi) Once again, a big round of applause for Mr. Arisugawa!

112
00:07:50,503 --> 00:07:57,003
(applause)

113
00:07:59,512 --> 00:08:02,015
《Ah, Kurosaki-san》

114
00:08:02,015 --> 00:08:05,018
Mr. Arisugawa, thank you for your hard work.

115
00:08:05,018 --> 00:08:08,521
Thank you for your wonderful performance.

116
00:08:08,521 --> 00:08:13,026
I was happy to be able to play this role.

117
00:08:13,026 --> 00:08:17,030
Arisugawa-san is so ephemeral that you can't even imagine it from her usual self➡

118
00:08:17,030 --> 00:08:20,033
She was exactly the heroine I had imagined.

119
00:08:20,033 --> 00:08:21,534
(Arisugawa) Hehe.

120
00:08:21,534 --> 00:08:23,536
Huh? Are you praising me for that?

121
00:08:23,536 --> 00:08:25,538
(laughter)

122
00:08:25,538 --> 00:08:29,042
Sorry. It's just a joke.

123
00:08:29,042 --> 00:08:31,044
Eh, this work is➡

124
00:08:31,044 --> 00:08:33,980
It will also be shown at film festivals overseas➡

125
00:08:33,980 --> 00:08:35,982
Me along with the work➡

126
00:08:35,982 --> 00:08:39,486
I want to spread my wings around the world.

127
00:08:39,486 --> 00:08:43,990
(applause)

128
00:08:43,990 --> 00:08:47,994
Director: Now we have no choice but to win this award.

129
00:08:47,994 --> 00:08:50,997
(Yanagi) Well, I'm in trouble.

130
00:08:50,997 --> 00:08:55,502
(people talking)

131
00:08:55,502 --> 00:08:57,504
⚟Please come again next time⚞

132
00:08:57,504 --> 00:09:01,007
(Yanagi) Let's do it again. (Laughter)

133
00:09:01,007 --> 00:09:05,007
《I really feel out of place》

134
00:09:06,513 --> 00:09:08,515
《No, why are you depressed? 》

135
00:09:08,515 --> 00:09:11,017
《To be invited to such an amazing place》

136
00:09:11,017 --> 00:09:13,019
I am absolutely ecstatic.

137
00:09:13,019 --> 00:09:17,023
《You must be happy just to see the wonderful Kurosaki-san》

138
00:09:17,023 --> 00:09:28,034
♬～

139
00:09:28,034 --> 00:09:29,536
Beat！

140
00:09:29,536 --> 00:09:31,538
Come join me soon.

141
00:09:31,538 --> 00:09:33,039
Arisugawa-san, I'm sorry, but...

142
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:37,477
(Hikaru) Is that the case with Arisugawa-san and CURO?

143
00:09:37,477 --> 00:09:39,479
(Wakana) It smells like Minster, right?

144
00:09:39,479 --> 00:09:42,482
That feeling definitely goes hand in hand.

145
00:09:42,482 --> 00:09:45,985
(Hikaru) You look good together, do you want to celebrate that?

146
00:09:45,985 --> 00:09:47,985
(Wakana) The best.

147
00:09:48,988 --> 00:09:53,993
《No way, people will misunderstand that we are lovers➡

148
00:09:53,993 --> 00:09:57,497
I've been told that I look good on you》

149
00:09:57,497 --> 00:10:02,001
《There's someone other than me... the one next to Kurosaki-san》

150
00:10:02,001 --> 00:10:05,004
《Even though we are not lovers➡

151
00:10:05,004 --> 00:10:08,004
I find myself thinking this too.

152
00:10:09,509 --> 00:10:11,009
《Nope》

153
00:10:13,513 --> 00:10:15,515
(Sound of door opening and closing)

154
00:10:15,515 --> 00:10:17,515
Sorry!

155
00:10:25,525 --> 00:10:27,026
(Kiriya) Kurosaki.

156
00:10:27,026 --> 00:10:29,529
Ah, Kiriya-san, that Koharu-san...

157
00:10:29,529 --> 00:10:32,031
Sorry.

158
00:10:32,031 --> 00:10:34,467
I thought it would distract reporters➡

159
00:10:34,467 --> 00:10:37,470
He did something that stirred up the Arisugawa River.

160
00:10:37,470 --> 00:10:38,970
picture…?

161
00:10:41,474 --> 00:10:46,479
"I thought I wouldn't lose, but I guess I'm not good at all."

162
00:10:46,479 --> 00:10:49,482
《Staying in circles all the time》

163
00:10:49,482 --> 00:10:52,986
((Koharu-san is my goddess))

164
00:10:52,986 --> 00:10:55,989
《What makes me a goddess?》

165
00:10:55,989 --> 00:10:59,492
(Arisugawa) I've sneaked into this place.

166
00:10:59,492 --> 00:11:01,494
You kinda got it, right?

167
00:11:01,494 --> 00:11:04,998
Who is suitable for CURO?

168
00:11:04,998 --> 00:11:09,498
Even at Minster, everyone is supporting us.

169
00:11:11,004 --> 00:11:15,508
But... that photo is a lie!

170
00:11:15,508 --> 00:11:19,512
Yes, the fans just misunderstood.

171
00:11:19,512 --> 00:11:23,016
But it's a good advertisement for the movie➡

172
00:11:23,016 --> 00:11:27,020
CURO's reputation has also increased because it has managed to land a popular actress.

173
00:11:27,020 --> 00:11:31,524
Hehe, even if you are a negative presence for CURO➡

174
00:11:31,524 --> 00:11:34,424
I can be a plus.

175
00:11:35,962 --> 00:11:38,965
If you're thinking about CURO, give up.

176
00:11:38,965 --> 00:11:40,967
Me too, for business➡

177
00:11:40,967 --> 00:11:43,469
I'm dating CURO.

178
00:11:43,469 --> 00:11:44,971
picture?

179
00:11:44,971 --> 00:11:46,973
I like novels, but➡

180
00:11:46,973 --> 00:11:49,976
I had no idea that CURO was such a boring guy.

181
00:11:49,976 --> 00:11:54,480
He doesn't seem to have any love experience and has bad taste in women.

182
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:59,986
But, well, it looks nice and I want the specs.

183
00:11:59,986 --> 00:12:02,986
I'll close my eyes at the lack of content.

184
00:12:05,992 --> 00:12:09,495
Kurosaki-san is certainly beautiful.

185
00:12:09,495 --> 00:12:12,498
Huh, beautiful?

186
00:12:12,498 --> 00:12:17,503
His novels are very popular, and he's rich.

187
00:12:17,503 --> 00:12:21,007
I think it's really amazing.

188
00:12:21,007 --> 00:12:23,009
((Can I have that?))

189
00:12:23,009 --> 00:12:25,011
((I'll crush you with everything I have!))

190
00:12:25,011 --> 00:12:27,013
((Fang of Justice!)) ((Wow!))

191
00:12:27,013 --> 00:12:31,517
((I want to have my first and last love with Koharu-san))

192
00:12:31,517 --> 00:12:35,417
But... that's not all.

193
00:12:36,956 --> 00:12:39,456
That can't be the only thing.

194
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,962
I don't understand how wonderful Kurosaki-san is➡

195
00:12:42,962 --> 00:12:45,465
You are the boring one!

196
00:12:45,465 --> 00:12:50,465
I will never give up the seat next to Kurosaki-san to you!

197
00:12:51,971 --> 00:12:55,471
No matter how many times I say it, you don't understand, you're an idiot!

198
00:12:59,479 --> 00:13:00,979
《Huh? 》

199
00:13:06,986 --> 00:13:15,495
♬～

200
00:13:15,495 --> 00:13:17,497
Beat…｡

201
00:13:17,497 --> 00:13:20,500
Ah... I'm sorry.

202
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:22,001
I stumbled.

203
00:13:22,001 --> 00:13:24,504
Mr. Arisugawa.

204
00:13:24,504 --> 00:13:27,507
I saw the photo of Minster.

205
00:13:27,507 --> 00:13:31,010
Ah... ah, that photo?

206
00:13:31,010 --> 00:13:34,947
There seems to be a rumor that we are lovers➡

207
00:13:34,947 --> 00:13:37,450
That's good news for you too, right?

208
00:13:37,450 --> 00:13:41,954
If we become lovers, the movie is sure to be a big hit.

209
00:13:41,954 --> 00:13:46,954
You can become famous not only in Japan but all over the world.

210
00:13:48,461 --> 00:13:50,463
So choose me?

211
00:13:50,463 --> 00:13:54,463
Shall we announce it in front of everyone after this?

212
00:13:55,468 --> 00:13:58,468
Well, let's do that.

213
00:13:59,972 --> 00:14:01,972
Mr. Kurosaki...

214
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:11,484
I apologize for interrupting your conversation.

215
00:14:11,484 --> 00:14:14,487
Please take this opportunity to inform everyone.

216
00:14:14,487 --> 00:14:17,990
⚟No way! ⚞ ⚟Not marriage⁉⚞

217
00:14:17,990 --> 00:14:22,490
It seems like there are rumors about us all over the place...

218
00:14:23,496 --> 00:14:26,999
I am Arisugawa-san…➡

219
00:14:26,999 --> 00:14:31,504
Instead, I've always been in love with another woman.

220
00:14:31,504 --> 00:14:34,440
(buzz)

221
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:37,944
The rumors about Mr. Arisugawa are groundless.

222
00:14:37,944 --> 00:14:43,444
Even if flowers bloom on stones, even if the earth turns backwards...

223
00:14:46,953 --> 00:14:49,956
Choosing someone other than her➡

224
00:14:49,956 --> 00:14:52,458
There is no eternal future.

225
00:14:52,458 --> 00:14:55,461
Mr. Arisugawa is also thinking about the movie➡

226
00:14:55,461 --> 00:14:58,965
I don't think they could deny the rumors.

227
00:14:58,965 --> 00:15:01,467
As I said earlier, I just look good➡

228
00:15:01,467 --> 00:15:05,471
You said that he was a man without substance.

229
00:15:05,471 --> 00:15:07,974
It was, right?

230
00:15:07,974 --> 00:15:11,978
Ha... I'm praising her appearance, right?

231
00:15:11,978 --> 00:15:14,480
(laughter)

232
00:15:14,480 --> 00:15:16,482
That's why➡

233
00:15:16,482 --> 00:15:19,982
Please do not misunderstand.

234
00:15:23,990 --> 00:15:26,990
Shirase-san, come here.

235
00:15:28,494 --> 00:15:31,994
(applause)

236
00:15:34,500 --> 00:15:38,003
Mr. Arisugawa, your talent is amazing➡

237
00:15:38,003 --> 00:15:40,506
Thank you for your efforts in preparing for the role➡

238
00:15:40,506 --> 00:15:42,508
I am grateful.

239
00:15:42,508 --> 00:15:44,508
But…｡

240
00:15:47,513 --> 00:15:49,513
It's too much.

241
00:15:51,016 --> 00:15:55,454
You heard everything, right? yes.

242
00:15:55,454 --> 00:15:59,454
If I were to do anything more to her...

243
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:03,462
I consider you an enemy.

244
00:16:03,462 --> 00:16:12,471
♬～

245
00:16:12,471 --> 00:16:14,471
I understand.

246
00:16:16,475 --> 00:16:19,478
but….

247
00:16:19,478 --> 00:16:24,984
It's true that I like CURO's novels.

248
00:16:24,984 --> 00:16:26,984
(Kiriya) I know.

249
00:16:28,988 --> 00:16:30,990
Thoughts on my debut work ➡

250
00:16:30,990 --> 00:16:33,990
You posted it on Minster.

251
00:16:36,996 --> 00:16:39,999
Even if I don't have that kind of scandal➡

252
00:16:39,999 --> 00:16:43,502
I believe this work will be widely accepted around the world.

253
00:16:43,502 --> 00:16:46,505
With the original...➡

254
00:16:46,505 --> 00:16:50,005
Arisugawa-san's acting is wonderful.

255
00:16:52,945 --> 00:16:58,450
If you'd like, please leave a comment for the next work.

256
00:16:58,450 --> 00:17:00,953
If you know that you are building a good relationship➡

257
00:17:00,953 --> 00:17:03,455
I think it will be a plus for Mr. Arisugawa as well.

258
00:17:03,455 --> 00:17:05,955
I understand.

259
00:17:07,459 --> 00:17:12,959
But... I only write my true feelings.

260
00:17:14,466 --> 00:17:16,966
Please create a good work.

261
00:17:18,470 --> 00:17:21,970
We will do our best to meet your expectations.

262
00:17:25,477 --> 00:17:27,479
I'm looking forward to it.

263
00:17:27,479 --> 00:17:35,988
♬～

264
00:17:35,988 --> 00:17:39,491
Sigh... you...

265
00:17:39,491 --> 00:17:42,494
If you're going to say it so clearly, please say something in advance!

266
00:17:42,494 --> 00:17:45,497
Sorry, I couldn't wrap my head around that much.

267
00:17:45,497 --> 00:17:47,499
Anyway…➡

268
00:17:47,499 --> 00:17:51,003
How could you say something like that in front of people?

269
00:17:51,003 --> 00:17:54,403
Is this also thanks to her?

270
00:17:55,441 --> 00:17:57,443
a….

271
00:17:57,443 --> 00:17:59,943
That may be so.

272
00:18:04,450 --> 00:18:06,952
I'll make you wait in the parking lot.

273
00:18:06,952 --> 00:18:10,456
It'll be troublesome if you get noticed, so give me a ride.

274
00:18:10,456 --> 00:18:12,958
Eh, but when we meet alone...

275
00:18:12,958 --> 00:18:16,462
It's better than making such a fuss.

276
00:18:16,462 --> 00:18:18,464
however!

277
00:18:18,464 --> 00:18:21,464
Do you maintain moderation?

278
00:18:22,968 --> 00:18:24,468
yes.

279
00:18:31,477 --> 00:18:32,978
Mr. Koharu.

280
00:18:32,978 --> 00:18:34,980
Ah, Kurosaki-san.

281
00:18:34,980 --> 00:18:37,483
I'll drive you home. Huh?

282
00:18:37,483 --> 00:18:39,483
Here it is.

283
00:18:43,489 --> 00:18:45,491
please.

284
00:18:45,491 --> 00:18:47,991
Sorry to bother you...

285
00:18:53,432 --> 00:18:55,432
Close it.

286
00:18:59,438 --> 00:19:00,938
(sound of car door closing)

287
00:19:04,943 --> 00:19:07,946
Is it okay to go home now?

288
00:19:07,946 --> 00:19:11,450
Ah... I told you that my clothes were dirty.

289
00:19:11,450 --> 00:19:14,453
I'm sorry for protecting me.

290
00:19:14,453 --> 00:19:16,955
Ah, no.

291
00:19:16,955 --> 00:19:19,458
About the rumors with Arisugawa-san➡

292
00:19:19,458 --> 00:19:22,461
I made you feel bad without realizing it➡

293
00:19:22,461 --> 00:19:24,463
I'm really sorry.

294
00:19:24,463 --> 00:19:26,465
Please don't apologize.

295
00:19:26,465 --> 00:19:28,467
I just cared too much.

296
00:19:28,467 --> 00:19:31,467
I also caused trouble for Kurosaki-san.

297
00:19:39,978 --> 00:19:41,978
It's okay.

298
00:19:43,482 --> 00:19:46,482
You can cause as much trouble as you want.

299
00:19:47,986 --> 00:19:51,486
Koharu-san, please.

300
00:19:55,928 --> 00:19:59,928
Please be kind to me?

301
00:20:04,937 --> 00:20:07,439
Mr. Koharu?

302
00:20:07,439 --> 00:20:09,942
Sorry, something happened...

303
00:20:09,942 --> 00:20:13,942
《You're giving me trouble, I have to stop it》

304
00:20:15,447 --> 00:20:20,452
If your hidden feelings turn into tears and overflow ➡

305
00:20:20,452 --> 00:20:23,956
Please don't stop.

306
00:20:23,956 --> 00:20:32,464
♬～

307
00:20:32,464 --> 00:20:34,464
I….

308
00:20:36,969 --> 00:20:39,469
I've always hated it.

309
00:20:41,473 --> 00:20:47,973
Mr. Arisugawa is clingy to Mr. Kurosaki.

310
00:20:50,482 --> 00:20:53,919
At a launch event like Minster➡

311
00:20:53,919 --> 00:20:57,419
Even when people say you look good together.

312
00:20:59,424 --> 00:21:01,924
Mr. Kurosaki...

313
00:21:04,429 --> 00:21:09,434
She said I was nice➡

314
00:21:09,434 --> 00:21:11,937
Not at all for Kurosaki-san➡

315
00:21:11,937 --> 00:21:15,941
I thought it wasn't balanced...

316
00:21:15,941 --> 00:21:21,941
I've been filled with a vague feeling...

317
00:21:24,950 --> 00:21:29,955
I hate myself for thinking like that...

318
00:21:29,955 --> 00:21:34,455
Kurosaki-san would be disappointed too.

319
00:21:35,961 --> 00:21:38,961
There's no way I'll be disappointed.

320
00:21:42,968 --> 00:21:48,473
Koharu-san is trying not to worry others➡

321
00:21:48,473 --> 00:21:54,413
I try to carry my weaknesses and hardships alone.

322
00:21:54,413 --> 00:21:59,913
I love your kindness.

323
00:22:03,922 --> 00:22:06,925
Don't hold back anymore.

324
00:22:06,925 --> 00:22:10,429
Your true feelings➡

325
00:22:10,429 --> 00:22:13,429
Please give it to me.

326
00:22:15,934 --> 00:22:20,934
Because I want to accept everything about you.

327
00:22:24,443 --> 00:22:28,443
Is it really okay to be pampered...?

328
00:22:29,948 --> 00:22:31,948
Of course.

329
00:22:35,454 --> 00:22:45,464
(cry)

330
00:22:45,464 --> 00:22:49,468
《Mr. Kurosaki saw me crying➡

331
00:22:49,468 --> 00:22:54,406
He kept stroking me with his big warm hands.

332
00:22:54,406 --> 00:22:59,411
《Maybe I have already➡

333
00:22:59,411 --> 00:23:01,911
To Mr. Kurosaki...》
